<a href="/questions/251317-is-this-book-an-exercise-in-religious">Is this book an exercise in religious bigotry against the bible and Judaism? It is ridiculing Judaism?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_251317'><a id="like_count_community_question_251317" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/251317?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">10 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F495395.The_Year_of_Living_Biblically">like</a></span>

